name: Tie Dye Digital Paper
description:
Tie Dye Digital Paper

These Tie-Dye digital papers are perfect for – larger areas eg fabrics for clothing, duvet covers, cushion covers etc, as well as other materials such as wallpaper, notebooks, invitations, gift tags, scrapbooking, wall art, stickers etc.

“The only limit is at the boundaries of your imagination” so have fun!,

FILES INCLUDED: ZIP FOLDER

– 28 JPG Files ( High Resolution)

SPECIFICATION :

– 3000×2000 px ( Background Size )

– 300 DPI Resolution

– RGB Color

Compatible with any software that allows you to work with jpg files and levels.
